cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV, cs.DC

This paper is about a framework for automatically learning ensembles using neural networks. The most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning) as the paper focuses on developing a framework for learning high-quality ensembles with minimal expert intervention. Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as the paper deals with neural networks and their structure. Additionally, cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) are also possible sub-categories as the paper discusses the use of distributed hardware for efficient training.
